name: Warmup_Div04_Sub03
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD4S3.CPF,
GmailD4S3.NOME,
GmailD4S3.EMAIL,
GmailD4S3.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD4S3.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD4S3.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD4S3.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD4S3.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV04_SUB03 GmailD4S3
UNION
